        <updateDate>2021-06-16T18:50:21Z</updateDate>
        <text>
          <![CDATA[ <p><b>Future Logging Careers Act </b></p> <p>This bill allows individuals who are 16 or 17 years old to work at certain logging operations that are owned or operated by at least one parent or a person standing in place of a parent. Thus, the bill exempts such employees from child labor laws.</p>]]>
        </text>
      </summary>
